---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  lang="de"
  title="Preise - AIVancePro | Kostenlos, Pro und Elite Pl&auml;ne"
  description="Entdecken Sie die AIVancePro Preise. Kostenloser Plan, Pro f&uuml;r 4,99&euro;/Monat und Elite f&uuml;r 7,99&euro;/Monat. Vergleichen Sie die Funktionen und w&auml;hlen Sie Ihren Plan."
  canonical="https://aivancepro.fr/de/preise/"
  alternates={{ fr: 'https://aivancepro.fr/pricing/', en: 'https://aivancepro.fr/en/pricing/', de: 'https://aivancepro.fr/de/preise/' }}
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <style>
      .pricing-hero {
          padding: 8rem 2rem 4rem;
          text-align: center;
          background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--gray-50) 0%, var(--white) 100%);
      }
      .pricing-hero h1 {
          font-size: 3rem;
          font-weight: 900;
          letter-spacing: -0.03em;
          color: var(--gray-900);
          margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      .pricing-hero h1 .gradient {
          background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue), var(--purple));
          -webkit-background-clip: text;
          -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
          background-clip: text;
      }
      .pricing-hero p {
          font-size: 1.15rem;
          color: var(--gray-500);
          max-width: 550px;
          margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .pricing-section { padding: 3rem 2rem 5rem; }
      .pricing-grid {
          max-width: 1100px;
          margin: 0 auto;
          display: grid;
          grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
          gap: 2rem;
          align-items: start;
      }
      .pricing-card {
          background: var(--white);
          border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
          border-radius: 20px;
          padding: 2.5rem;
          position: relative;
          transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
      }
      .pricing-card:hover {
          transform: translateY(-4px);
          box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      }
      .pricing-card.featured {
          border-color: var(--blue);
          box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1);
      }
      .pricing-card.featured::before {
          content: 'Beliebt';
          position: absolute;
          top: -12px;
          left: 50%;
          transform: translateX(-50%);
          background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue), var(--purple));
          color: var(--white);
          font-size: 0.75rem;
          font-weight: 700;
          padding: 0.3rem 1rem;
          border-radius: 50px;
      }
      .plan-name { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gray-900); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
      .price { font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--gray-900); letter-spacing: -0.03em; }
      .price span { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--gray-500); }
      .price-desc { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--gray-500); margin-bottom: 2rem; }
      .pricing-features { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
      .pricing-features li { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--gray-700); }
      .pricing-features li svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; color: var(--blue); flex-shrink: 0; }
      .pricing-features li.disabled { color: var(--gray-400); }
      .pricing-features li.disabled svg { color: var(--gray-300); }
      .btn-pricing { display: block; width: 100%; text-align: center; padding: 0.875rem; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s; }
      .btn-pricing.primary { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue), var(--purple)); color: var(--white); box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.25); }
      .btn-pricing.primary:hover { opacity: 0.92; transform: translateY(-2px); }
      .btn-pricing.outline { background: var(--white); color: var(--gray-700); border: 1px solid var(--gray-200); }
      .btn-pricing.outline:hover { border-color: var(--blue); color: var(--blue); }
      .comparison-section { padding: 5rem 2rem; background: var(--gray-50); }
      .comparison-section h2 { text-align: center; font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 3rem; color: var(--gray-900); }
      .comparison-table { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; background: var(--white); border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04); }
      .comparison-table th, .comparison-table td { padding: 1rem 1.25rem; text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-100); font-size: 0.9rem; }
      .comparison-table th { background: var(--gray-900); color: var(--white); font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.85rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
      .comparison-table th:first-child { text-align: left; }
      .comparison-table td:first-child { text-align: left; font-weight: 500; color: var(--gray-700); }
      .comparison-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
      .comparison-table .check { color: var(--green); font-size: 1.2rem; }
      .comparison-table .cross { color: var(--gray-300); font-size: 1rem; }
      .faq-section { padding: 5rem 2rem; }
      .faq-section h2 { text-align: center; font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 3rem; color: var(--gray-900); }
      .faq-list { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
      .faq-item { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-200); }
      .faq-question { width: 100%; background: none; border: none; text-align: left; padding: 1.5rem 0; font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--gray-900); cursor: pointer; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; font-family: inherit; transition: color 0.2s; }
      .faq-question:hover { color: var(--blue); }
      .faq-question svg { width: 20px; height: 20px; color: var(--gray-400); transition: transform 0.3s; flex-shrink: 0; }
      .faq-item.open .faq-question svg { transform: rotate(180deg); }
      .faq-answer { max-height: 0; overflow: hidden; transition: max-height 0.3s ease; }
      .faq-answer-inner { padding: 0 0 1.5rem; font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--gray-500); line-height: 1.7; }
      .faq-item.open .faq-answer { max-height: 300px; }
      @media (max-width: 768px) {
          .pricing-hero h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
          .pricing-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
          .comparison-table { font-size: 0.8rem; }
          .comparison-table th, .comparison-table td { padding: 0.75rem 0.5rem; }
      }
    </style>
  </Fragment>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="pricing-hero">
        <h1>W&auml;hlen Sie Ihren <span class="gradient">Plan</span></h1>
        <p>Starten Sie kostenlos, dann wechseln Sie zu Pro oder Elite, um das volle Potenzial Ihres Trainings freizuschalten.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Pricing Cards -->
    <section class="pricing-section">
        <div class="pricing-grid">
            <div class="pricing-card">
                <div class="plan-name">Kostenlos</div>
                <div class="price">0&euro; <span>/ Monat</span></div>
                <div class="price-desc">Zum Entdecken der App</div>
                <ul class="pricing-features">
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Aufzeichnung der Trainingseinheiten</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Grundlegendes Fortschrittstracking</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Community-Zugang</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>3 KI-Nachrichten / Monat</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="https://apps.apple.com/app/aivancepro/id6756116760" class="btn-pricing outline" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Kostenlos starten</a>
            </div>
            <div class="pricing-card featured">
                <div class="plan-name">Pro</div>
                <div class="price">4,99&euro; <span>/ Monat</span></div>
                <div class="price-desc">F&uuml;r ernsthaften Fortschritt</div>
                <ul class="pricing-features">
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Alles aus Free +</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>150 KI-Nachrichten / Monat</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>KI-Trainingsgenerierung</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Trainingsplan (4 Wochen)</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Gruppen &amp; Challenges erstellen</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Erweiterte Analysen</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="/de/login/" class="btn-pricing primary">Pro abonnieren</a>
            </div>
            <div class="pricing-card">
                <div class="plan-name">Elite</div>
                <div class="price">7,99&euro; <span>/ Monat</span></div>
                <div class="price-desc">Das komplette Erlebnis</div>
                <ul class="pricing-features">
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Unbegrenzte KI-Nachrichten</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>KI-Trainingsgenerierung</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Trainingspl&auml;ne (bis zu 12 Wochen)</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Gruppen &amp; Challenges erstellen</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Erweiterte Analysen</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>&Uuml;bertrainingsanalyse</li>
                    <li><svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>Priorit&auml;ts-Support</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="/de/login/" class="btn-pricing primary" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #9333EA, #6D28D9);">Elite abonnieren</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Comparison Table -->
    <section class="comparison-section">
        <h2>Detaillierter Vergleich</h2>
        <table class="comparison-table">
            <thead><tr><th>Funktion</th><th>Kostenlos</th><th>Pro</th><th>Elite</th></tr></thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr><td>Aufzeichnung der Trainingseinheiten</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Grundlegendes Fortschrittstracking</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Community-Zugang</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td></tr>
                <tr><td>KI-Nachrichten</td><td>3 / Monat</td><td>150 / Monat</td><td>Unbegrenzt</td></tr>
                <tr><td>KI-Trainingsgenerierung</td><td class="cross">&mdash;</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Trainingsplan</td><td class="cross">&mdash;</td><td>4 Wochen</td><td>Bis zu 12 Wochen</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Gruppen &amp; Challenges erstellen</td><td class="cross">&mdash;</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Erweiterte Analysen</td><td class="cross">&mdash;</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td></tr>
                <tr><td>&Uuml;bertrainingsanalyse</td><td class="cross">&mdash;</td><td class="cross">&mdash;</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td></tr>
                <tr><td>Priorit&auml;ts-Support</td><td class="cross">&mdash;</td><td class="cross">&mdash;</td><td class="check">&#10003;</td></tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Pricing -->
    <section class="faq-section">
        <h2>H&auml;ufig gestellte Fragen zu den Preisen</h2>
        <div class="faq-list">
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                    Kann ich jederzeit den Plan wechseln?
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.23 7.21a.75.75 0 011.06.02L10 11.168l3.71-3.938a.75.75 0 111.08 1.04l-4.25 4.5a.75.75 0 01-1.08 0l-4.25-4.5a.75.75 0 01.02-1.06z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Ja, Sie k&ouml;nnen jederzeit von Pro zu Elite wechseln oder herabstufen. Die &Auml;nderung wird sofort wirksam.</div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                    Gibt es eine Vertragsbindung?
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.23 7.21a.75.75 0 011.06.02L10 11.168l3.71-3.938a.75.75 0 111.08 1.04l-4.25 4.5a.75.75 0 01-1.08 0l-4.25-4.5a.75.75 0 01.02-1.06z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Keine Vertragsbindung. Sie k&ouml;nnen Ihr Abonnement jederzeit &uuml;ber den App Store oder Google Play k&uuml;ndigen.</div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                    Ist der kostenlose Plan wirklich kostenlos?
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.23 7.21a.75.75 0 011.06.02L10 11.168l3.71-3.938a.75.75 0 111.08 1.04l-4.25 4.5a.75.75 0 01-1.08 0l-4.25-4.5a.75.75 0 01.02-1.06z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Absolut. Der kostenlose Plan gibt Ihnen Zugang zum Trainings-Tracking, zu &uuml;ber 240 &Uuml;bungen und zu Basis-Statistiken, ohne Zeitlimit und ohne Kreditkarte.</div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                    Wie funktioniert die Zahlung?
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.23 7.21a.75.75 0 011.06.02L10 11.168l3.71-3.938a.75.75 0 111.08 1.04l-4.25 4.5a.75.75 0 01-1.08 0l-4.25-4.5a.75.75 0 01.02-1.06z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Die Zahlung wird direkt &uuml;ber den App Store (iOS) oder Google Play (Android) abgewickelt. Ihr Abonnement verl&auml;ngert sich automatisch jeden Monat, sofern Sie es nicht k&uuml;ndigen.</div></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>
